Detailed Description

The logger module is responsible for creating replay files.

The logger will save events coming from the network, zcamera, falcon and user interface module. These events are saved in a file so that the replayer can replay those events. The logger can also output in a human readable output.

enum LogEvent::LogEventEnum

package This enum represents all input events that the system can receive.

These include inputs from the network, the user interface, the falcon and the zcamera.
